This paper focuses on the development of a wearable system for long-term lifelogging, which involves the use of energy harvesting technologies as a means of sustainable energy source. The paper also proposes a place recognition method based on machine learning. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), followed by Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves data analysis and modeling, which could fall under Statistical Learning (cs.SD) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
